m> pink-coloured rod).</s></p><p class="description"><s>Rod-shaped cells, non-motile by gliding.</s><s>Gram-negative.</s><s>Does not form endospores.</s><s>Strictly aerobic.</s><s>Produces non-diffusible carotenoid pigments.</s><s>Chemo-organotrophs.</s><s>Cytochrome oxidase-, catalase- and alkaline phosphatase-positive.</s><s>The major respiratory quinone is MK-7.</s><s>The main cellular fatty acids are straight-chain unsaturated and branched-chain unsaturated fatty acids i15 : 1, i15 : 0, a15 : 0 and i17 : 0 3-OH.</s><s>16S rRNA gene sequence analysis indicates that the genus <em>Roseivirga</em> is a member of the phylum ‘<em>Bacteroidetes</em>’.</s><s>The type species is <em>Roseivirga ehrenbergii</em>.</s></p></content></protolog>